        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1350" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1350"></td>
          <td id="LC1350" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As is a winged messenger of heaven</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1351" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1351"></td>
          <td id="LC1351" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Unto the white-upturned wond&#39;ring eyes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1352" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1352"></td>
          <td id="LC1352" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of mortals that fall back to gaze on him</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1353" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1353"></td>
          <td id="LC1353" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    When he bestrides the lazy-pacing clouds</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1354" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1354"></td>
          <td id="LC1354" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And sails upon the bosom of the air.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1355" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1355"></td>
          <td id="LC1355" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1356" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1356"></td>
          <td id="LC1356" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. O Romeo, Romeo! wherefore art thou Romeo?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1357" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1357"></td>
          <td id="LC1357" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Deny thy father and refuse thy name!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1358" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1358"></td>
          <td id="LC1358" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or, if thou wilt not, be but sworn my love,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1359" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1359"></td>
          <td id="LC1359" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And I&#39;ll no longer be a Capulet.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1360" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1360"></td>
          <td id="LC1360" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1361" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1361"></td>
          <td id="LC1361" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. [aside] Shall I hear more, or shall I speak at this?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1362" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1362"></td>
          <td id="LC1362" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1363" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1363"></td>
          <td id="LC1363" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. &#39;Tis but thy name that is my enemy.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1364" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1364"></td>
          <td id="LC1364" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou art thyself, though not a Montague.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1365" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1365"></td>
          <td id="LC1365" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What&#39;s Montague? it is nor hand, nor foot,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1366" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1366"></td>
          <td id="LC1366" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Nor arm, nor face, nor any other part</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1367" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1367"></td>
          <td id="LC1367" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Belonging to a man. O, be some other name!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1368" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1368"></td>
          <td id="LC1368" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What&#39;s in a name? That which we call a rose</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1369" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1369"></td>
          <td id="LC1369" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By any other name would smell as sweet.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1370" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1370"></td>
          <td id="LC1370" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    So Romeo would, were he not Romeo call&#39;d,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1371" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1371"></td>
          <td id="LC1371" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Retain that dear perfection which he owes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1372" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1372"></td>
          <td id="LC1372" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Without that title. Romeo, doff thy name;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1373" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1373"></td>
          <td id="LC1373" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And for that name, which is no part of thee,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1374" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1374"></td>
          <td id="LC1374" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Take all myself.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1375" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1375"></td>
          <td id="LC1375" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1376" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1376"></td>
          <td id="LC1376" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. I take thee at thy word.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1377" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1377"></td>
          <td id="LC1377" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Call me but love, and I&#39;ll be new baptiz&#39;d;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1378" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1378"></td>
          <td id="LC1378" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Henceforth I never will be Romeo.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1379" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1379"></td>
          <td id="LC1379" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1380" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1380"></td>
          <td id="LC1380" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. What man art thou that, thus bescreen&#39;d in night,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1381" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1381"></td>
          <td id="LC1381" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    So stumblest on my counsel?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1382" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1382"></td>
          <td id="LC1382" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1383" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1383"></td>
          <td id="LC1383" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. By a name</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1384" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1384"></td>
          <td id="LC1384" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I know not how to tell thee who I am.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1385" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1385"></td>
          <td id="LC1385" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My name, dear saint, is hateful to myself,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1386" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1386"></td>
          <td id="LC1386" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Because it is an enemy to thee.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1387" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1387"></td>
          <td id="LC1387" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Had I it written, I would tear the word.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1388" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1388"></td>
          <td id="LC1388" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1389" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1389"></td>
          <td id="LC1389" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. My ears have yet not drunk a hundred words</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1390" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1390"></td>
          <td id="LC1390" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of that tongue&#39;s utterance, yet I know the sound.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1391" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1391"></td>
          <td id="LC1391" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Art thou not Romeo, and a Montague?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1392" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1392"></td>
          <td id="LC1392" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1393" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1393"></td>
          <td id="LC1393" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Neither, fair saint, if either thee dislike.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1394" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1394"></td>
          <td id="LC1394" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1395" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1395"></td>
          <td id="LC1395" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. How cam&#39;st thou hither, tell me, and wherefore?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1396" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1396"></td>
          <td id="LC1396" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The orchard walls are high and hard to climb,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1397" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1397"></td>
          <td id="LC1397" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And the place death, considering who thou art,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1398" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1398"></td>
          <td id="LC1398" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If any of my kinsmen find thee here.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1399" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1399"></td>
          <td id="LC1399" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1400" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1400"></td>
          <td id="LC1400" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. With love&#39;s light wings did I o&#39;erperch these walls;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1401" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1401"></td>
          <td id="LC1401" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For stony limits cannot hold love out,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1402" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1402"></td>
          <td id="LC1402" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And what love can do, that dares love attempt.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1403" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1403"></td>
          <td id="LC1403" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Therefore thy kinsmen are no let to me.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1404" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1404"></td>
          <td id="LC1404" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1405" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1405"></td>
          <td id="LC1405" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. If they do see thee, they will murther thee.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1406" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1406"></td>
          <td id="LC1406" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1407" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1407"></td>
          <td id="LC1407" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Alack, there lies more peril in thine eye</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1408" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1408"></td>
          <td id="LC1408" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than twenty of their swords! Look thou but sweet,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1409" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1409"></td>
          <td id="LC1409" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And I am proof against their enmity.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1410" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1410"></td>
          <td id="LC1410" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1411" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1411"></td>
          <td id="LC1411" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. I would not for the world they saw thee here.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1412" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1412"></td>
          <td id="LC1412" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1413" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1413"></td>
          <td id="LC1413" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. I have night&#39;s cloak to hide me from their sight;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1414" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1414"></td>
          <td id="LC1414" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And but thou love me, let them find me here.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1415" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1415"></td>
          <td id="LC1415" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My life were better ended by their hate</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1416" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1416"></td>
          <td id="LC1416" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than death prorogued, wanting of thy love.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1417" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1417"></td>
          <td id="LC1417" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1418" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1418"></td>
          <td id="LC1418" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. By whose direction found&#39;st thou out this place?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1419" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1419"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC1420" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. By love, that first did prompt me to enquire.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1421" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1421"></td>
          <td id="LC1421" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    He lent me counsel, and I lent him eyes.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1422" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1422"></td>
          <td id="LC1422" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I am no pilot; yet, wert thou as far</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1423" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1423"></td>
          <td id="LC1423" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As that vast shore wash&#39;d with the farthest sea,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1424" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1424"></td>
          <td id="LC1424" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I would adventure for such merchandise.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1425" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1425"></td>
          <td id="LC1425" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1426" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1426"></td>
          <td id="LC1426" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Thou knowest the mask of night is on my face;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1427" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1427"></td>
          <td id="LC1427" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Else would a maiden blush bepaint my cheek</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1428" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1428"></td>
          <td id="LC1428" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For that which thou hast heard me speak to-night.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1429" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1429"></td>
          <td id="LC1429" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Fain would I dwell on form- fain, fain deny</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1430" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1430"></td>
          <td id="LC1430" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What I have spoke; but farewell compliment!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1431" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1431"></td>
          <td id="LC1431" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Dost thou love me, I know thou wilt say &#39;Ay&#39;;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1432" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1432"></td>
          <td id="LC1432" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And I will take thy word. Yet, if thou swear&#39;st,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1433" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1433"></td>
          <td id="LC1433" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou mayst prove false. At lovers&#39; perjuries,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1434" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1434"></td>
          <td id="LC1434" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    They say Jove laughs. O gentle Romeo,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1435" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1435"></td>
          <td id="LC1435" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If thou dost love, pronounce it faithfully.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1436" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1436"></td>
          <td id="LC1436" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or if thou thinkest I am too quickly won,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1437" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1437"></td>
          <td id="LC1437" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I&#39;ll frown, and be perverse, and say thee nay,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1438" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1438"></td>
          <td id="LC1438" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    So thou wilt woo; but else, not for the world.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1439" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1439"></td>
          <td id="LC1439" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In truth, fair Montague, I am too fond,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1440" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1440"></td>
          <td id="LC1440" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And therefore thou mayst think my haviour light;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1441" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1441"></td>
          <td id="LC1441" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But trust me, gentleman, I&#39;ll prove more true</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1442" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1442"></td>
          <td id="LC1442" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than those that have more cunning to be strange.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1443" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1443"></td>
          <td id="LC1443" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I should have been more strange, I must confess,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1444" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1444"></td>
          <td id="LC1444" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But that thou overheard&#39;st, ere I was ware,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1445" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1445"></td>
          <td id="LC1445" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My true-love passion. Therefore pardon me,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1446" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1446"></td>
          <td id="LC1446" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And not impute this yielding to light love,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1447" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1447"></td>
          <td id="LC1447" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which the dark night hath so discovered.</td>

        <tr>
          <td id="L1448" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1448"></td>
          <td id="LC1448" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1449" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1449"></td>
          <td id="LC1449" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Lady, by yonder blessed moon I swear,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1450" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1450"></td>
          <td id="LC1450" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That tips with silver all these fruit-tree tops-</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC1452" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. O, swear not by the moon, th&#39; inconstant moon,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1453" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1453"></td>
          <td id="LC1453" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That monthly changes in her circled orb,</td>

</td>

        </tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC1459" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or if thou wilt, swear by thy gracious self,</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC1463" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. If my heart&#39;s dear love-</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="L1464" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1464"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC1465" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Well, do not swear. Although I joy in thee,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1466" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1466"></td>
          <td id="LC1466" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I have no joy of this contract to-night.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1467" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It is too rash, too unadvis&#39;d, too sudden;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1468" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Too like the lightning, which doth cease to be</td>

          <td id="LC1469" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Ere one can say &#39;It lightens.&#39; Sweet, good night!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1470" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1470"></td>
          <td id="LC1470" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    This bud of love, by summer&#39;s ripening breath,</td>

        </tr>

</td>

</td>

        <tr>
          <td id="L1595" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1595"></td>
          <td id="LC1595" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. The grey-ey&#39;d morn smiles on the frowning night,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1596" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1596"></td>
          <td id="LC1596" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Check&#39;ring the Eastern clouds with streaks of light;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1597" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1597"></td>
          <td id="LC1597" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And flecked darkness like a drunkard reels</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1598" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1598"></td>
          <td id="LC1598" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    From forth day&#39;s path and Titan&#39;s fiery wheels.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1599" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1599"></td>
          <td id="LC1599" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Non, ere the sun advance his burning eye</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1600" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1600"></td>
          <td id="LC1600" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The day to cheer and night&#39;s dank dew to dry,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1601" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1601"></td>
          <td id="LC1601" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I must up-fill this osier cage of ours</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1602" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1602"></td>
          <td id="LC1602" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    With baleful weeds and precious-juiced flowers.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1603" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1603"></td>
          <td id="LC1603" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The earth that&#39;s nature&#39;s mother is her tomb.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1604" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1604"></td>
          <td id="LC1604" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What is her burying gave, that is her womb;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1605" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1605"></td>
          <td id="LC1605" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And from her womb children of divers kind</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1606" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1606"></td>
          <td id="LC1606" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    We sucking on her natural bosom find;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1607" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1607"></td>
          <td id="LC1607" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Many for many virtues excellent,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1608" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    None but for some, and yet all different.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1609" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1609"></td>
          <td id="LC1609" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O, mickle is the powerful grace that lies</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1610" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1610"></td>
          <td id="LC1610" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In plants, herbs, stones, and their true qualities;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1611" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1611"></td>
          <td id="LC1611" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For naught so vile that on the earth doth live</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1612" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1612"></td>
          <td id="LC1612" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But to the earth some special good doth give;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1613" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1613"></td>
          <td id="LC1613" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Nor aught so good but, strain&#39;d from that fair use,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1614" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1614"></td>
          <td id="LC1614" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Revolts from true birth, stumbling on abuse.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1615" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1615"></td>
          <td id="LC1615" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Virtue itself turns vice, being misapplied,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1616" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1616"></td>
          <td id="LC1616" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And vice sometime&#39;s by action dignified.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1617" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1617"></td>
          <td id="LC1617" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Within the infant rind of this small flower</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1618" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1618"></td>
          <td id="LC1618" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Poison hath residence, and medicine power;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1619" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1619"></td>
          <td id="LC1619" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For this, being smelt, with that part cheers each part;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1620" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1620"></td>
          <td id="LC1620" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Being tasted, slays all senses with the heart.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC1622" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In man as well as herbs- grace and rude will;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1623" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1623"></td>
          <td id="LC1623" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And where the worser is predominant,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1631" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Benedicite!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1632" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1632"></td>
          <td id="LC1632" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What early tongue so sweet saluteth me?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1633" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1633"></td>
          <td id="LC1633" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Young son, it argues a distempered head</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1634" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1634"></td>
          <td id="LC1634" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    So soon to bid good morrow to thy bed.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1635" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1635"></td>
          <td id="LC1635" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Care keeps his watch in every old man&#39;s eye,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1636" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1636"></td>
          <td id="LC1636" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And where care lodges sleep will never lie;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1637" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1637"></td>
          <td id="LC1637" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But where unbruised youth with unstuff&#39;d brain</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1638" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1638"></td>
          <td id="LC1638" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Doth couch his limbs, there golden sleep doth reign.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1639" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1639"></td>
          <td id="LC1639" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Therefore thy earliness doth me assure</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC1644" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. That last is true-the sweeter rest was mine.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>

        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC1648" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. With Rosaline, my ghostly father? No.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1649" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I have forgot that name, and that name&#39;s woe.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC1651" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. That&#39;s my good son! But where hast thou been then?</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC1653" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. I&#39;ll tell thee ere thou ask it me again.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1654" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1654"></td>
          <td id="LC1654" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I have been feasting with mine enemy,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1655" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1655"></td>
          <td id="LC1655" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where on a sudden one hath wounded me</td>

          <td id="LC1656" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That&#39;s by me wounded. Both our remedies</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1657" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Within thy help and holy physic lies.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1658" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1658"></td>
          <td id="LC1658" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I bear no hatred, blessed man, for, lo,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1659" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1659"></td>
          <td id="LC1659" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My intercession likewise steads my foe.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1660" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1660"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1661" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Be plain, good son, and homely in thy drift</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC1662" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Riddling confession finds but riddling shrift.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1663" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1663"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC1664" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Then plainly know my heart&#39;s dear love is set</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1665" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1665"></td>
          <td id="LC1665" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    On the fair daughter of rich Capulet;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1666" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1666"></td>
          <td id="LC1666" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As mine on hers, so hers is set on mine,</td>

          <td id="LC1667" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And all combin&#39;d, save what thou must combine</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1668" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1668"></td>
          <td id="LC1668" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By holy marriage. When, and where, and how</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1669" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1669"></td>
          <td id="LC1669" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    We met, we woo&#39;d, and made exchange of vow,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1670" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1670"></td>
          <td id="LC1670" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I&#39;ll tell thee as we pass; but this I pray,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1671" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1671"></td>
          <td id="LC1671" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That thou consent to marry us to-day.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1672" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1672"></td>
          <td id="LC1672" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1673" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1673"></td>
          <td id="LC1673" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Holy Saint Francis! What a change is here!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1674" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1674"></td>
          <td id="LC1674" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is Rosaline, that thou didst love so dear,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L1675" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="1675"></td>
          <td id="LC1675" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    So soon forsaken? Young men&#39;s love then lies</td>

          <td id="LC2254" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    minstrels of us, look to hear nothing but discords. Here&#39;s my</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2413" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2413"></td>
          <td id="LC2413" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2414" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2414"></td>
          <td id="LC2414" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Ben. O noble Prince. I can discover all</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2415" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2415"></td>
          <td id="LC2415" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The unlucky manage of this fatal brawl.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2416" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2416"></td>
          <td id="LC2416" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    There lies the man, slain by young Romeo,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2417" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2417"></td>
          <td id="LC2417" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That slew thy kinsman, brave Mercutio.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2418" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2418"></td>
          <td id="LC2418" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2419" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2419"></td>
          <td id="LC2419" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Cap. Wife. Tybalt, my cousin! O my brother&#39;s child!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2420" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2420"></td>
          <td id="LC2420" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O Prince! O husband! O, the blood is spill&#39;d</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2421" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2421"></td>
          <td id="LC2421" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of my dear kinsman! Prince, as thou art true,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2422" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2422"></td>
          <td id="LC2422" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For blood of ours shed blood of Montague.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2423" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2423"></td>
          <td id="LC2423" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O cousin, cousin!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2424" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2424"></td>
          <td id="LC2424" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2425" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2425"></td>
          <td id="LC2425" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. Benvolio, who began this bloody fray?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2426" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2426"></td>
          <td id="LC2426" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2427" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2427"></td>
          <td id="LC2427" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Ben. Tybalt, here slain, whom Romeo&#39;s hand did stay.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2428" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2428"></td>
          <td id="LC2428" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Romeo, that spoke him fair, bid him bethink</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2429" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2429"></td>
          <td id="LC2429" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    How nice the quarrel was, and urg&#39;d withal</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2430" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2430"></td>
          <td id="LC2430" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Your high displeasure. All this- uttered</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2431" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2431"></td>
          <td id="LC2431" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    With gentle breath, calm look, knees humbly bow&#39;d-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2432" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2432"></td>
          <td id="LC2432" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Could not take truce with the unruly spleen</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2433" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2433"></td>
          <td id="LC2433" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of Tybalt deaf to peace, but that he tilts</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2434" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2434"></td>
          <td id="LC2434" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    With piercing steel at bold Mercutio&#39;s breast;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2435" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2435"></td>
          <td id="LC2435" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Who, all as hot, turns deadly point to point,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2436" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2436"></td>
          <td id="LC2436" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And, with a martial scorn, with one hand beats</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2437" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2437"></td>
          <td id="LC2437" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Cold death aside and with the other sends</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2438" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2438"></td>
          <td id="LC2438" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It back to Tybalt, whose dexterity</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2439" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2439"></td>
          <td id="LC2439" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Retorts it. Romeo he cries aloud,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2440" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2440"></td>
          <td id="LC2440" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    &#39;Hold, friends! friends, part!&#39; and swifter than his tongue,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2441" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2441"></td>
          <td id="LC2441" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    His agile arm beats down their fatal points,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2442" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2442"></td>
          <td id="LC2442" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And &#39;twixt them rushes; underneath whose arm</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2443" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2443"></td>
          <td id="LC2443" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    An envious thrust from Tybalt hit the life</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2444" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2444"></td>
          <td id="LC2444" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of stout Mercutio, and then Tybalt fled;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2445" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2445"></td>
          <td id="LC2445" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But by-and-by comes back to Romeo,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2446" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2446"></td>
          <td id="LC2446" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Who had but newly entertain&#39;d revenge,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2447" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2447"></td>
          <td id="LC2447" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And to&#39;t they go like lightning; for, ere I</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2448" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2448"></td>
          <td id="LC2448" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Could draw to part them, was stout Tybalt slain;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2449" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2449"></td>
          <td id="LC2449" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And, as he fell, did Romeo turn and fly.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2450" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2450"></td>
          <td id="LC2450" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    This is the truth, or let Benvolio die.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2451" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2451"></td>
          <td id="LC2451" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2452" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2452"></td>
          <td id="LC2452" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Cap. Wife. He is a kinsman to the Montague;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2453" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2453"></td>
          <td id="LC2453" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Affection makes him false, he speaks not true.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2454" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2454"></td>
          <td id="LC2454" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Some twenty of them fought in this black strife,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2455" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2455"></td>
          <td id="LC2455" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And all those twenty could but kill one life.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2456" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2456"></td>
          <td id="LC2456" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I beg for justice, which thou, Prince, must give.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2457" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2457"></td>
          <td id="LC2457" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Romeo slew Tybalt; Romeo must not live.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2458" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2458"></td>
          <td id="LC2458" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2459" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2459"></td>
          <td id="LC2459" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. Romeo slew him; he slew Mercutio.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2460" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2460"></td>
          <td id="LC2460" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Who now the price of his dear blood doth owe?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2461" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2461"></td>
          <td id="LC2461" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2462" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2462"></td>
          <td id="LC2462" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Mon. Not Romeo, Prince; he was Mercutio&#39;s friend;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2463" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2463"></td>
          <td id="LC2463" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    His fault concludes but what the law should end,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2464" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2464"></td>
          <td id="LC2464" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The life of Tybalt.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2465" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2465"></td>
          <td id="LC2465" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2466" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2466"></td>
          <td id="LC2466" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. And for that offence</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2467" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2467"></td>
          <td id="LC2467" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Immediately we do exile him hence.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2468" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2468"></td>
          <td id="LC2468" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I have an interest in your hate&#39;s proceeding,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2469" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2469"></td>
          <td id="LC2469" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My blood for your rude brawls doth lie a-bleeding;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2470" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2470"></td>
          <td id="LC2470" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But I&#39;ll amerce you with so strong a fine</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2471" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2471"></td>
          <td id="LC2471" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That you shall all repent the loss of mine.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2472" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2472"></td>
          <td id="LC2472" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I will be deaf to pleading and excuses;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2473" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2473"></td>
          <td id="LC2473" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Nor tears nor prayers shall purchase out abuses.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2474" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2474"></td>
          <td id="LC2474" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Therefore use none. Let Romeo hence in haste,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2475" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2475"></td>
          <td id="LC2475" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Else, when he is found, that hour is his last.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2476" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2476"></td>
          <td id="LC2476" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Bear hence this body, and attend our will.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2477" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2477"></td>
          <td id="LC2477" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Mercy but murders, pardoning those that kill.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2478" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2478"></td>
          <td id="LC2478" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">                                                         Exeunt.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2479" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2479"></td>
          <td id="LC2479" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2480" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2480"></td>
          <td id="LC2480" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2481" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2481"></td>
          <td id="LC2481" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2482" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2482"></td>
          <td id="LC2482" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2483" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2483"></td>
          <td id="LC2483" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">Scene II.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2484" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2484"></td>
          <td id="LC2484" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">Capulet&#39;s orchard.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2485" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2485"></td>
          <td id="LC2485" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2486" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2486"></td>
          <td id="LC2486" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">Enter Juliet alone.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2487" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2487"></td>
          <td id="LC2487" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2488" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2488"></td>
          <td id="LC2488" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2489" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2489"></td>
          <td id="LC2489" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Gallop apace, you fiery-footed steeds,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2490" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2490"></td>
          <td id="LC2490" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Towards Phoebus&#39; lodging! Such a wagoner</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2491" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2491"></td>
          <td id="LC2491" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As Phaeton would whip you to the West</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2492" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2492"></td>
          <td id="LC2492" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And bring in cloudy night immediately.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2493" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2493"></td>
          <td id="LC2493" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Spread thy close curtain, love-performing night,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2494" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2494"></td>
          <td id="LC2494" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That runaway eyes may wink, and Romeo</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2495" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2495"></td>
          <td id="LC2495" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Leap to these arms untalk&#39;d of and unseen.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2496" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2496"></td>
          <td id="LC2496" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Lovers can see to do their amorous rites</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2497" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2497"></td>
          <td id="LC2497" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By their own beauties; or, if love be blind,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2498" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2498"></td>
          <td id="LC2498" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It best agrees with night. Come, civil night,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2499" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2499"></td>
          <td id="LC2499" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou sober-suited matron, all in black,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2500" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2500"></td>
          <td id="LC2500" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And learn me how to lose a winning match,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2501" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2501"></td>
          <td id="LC2501" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Play&#39;d for a pair of stainless maidenhoods.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2502" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2502"></td>
          <td id="LC2502" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hood my unmann&#39;d blood, bating in my cheeks,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2503" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2503"></td>
          <td id="LC2503" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    With thy black mantle till strange love, grown bold,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2504" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2504"></td>
          <td id="LC2504" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Think true love acted simple modesty.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2505" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2505"></td>
          <td id="LC2505" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Come, night; come, Romeo; come, thou day in night;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2506" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2506"></td>
          <td id="LC2506" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For thou wilt lie upon the wings of night</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2507" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2507"></td>
          <td id="LC2507" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Whiter than new snow upon a raven&#39;s back.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2508" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2508"></td>
          <td id="LC2508" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Come, gentle night; come, loving, black-brow&#39;d night;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2509" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2509"></td>
          <td id="LC2509" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Give me my Romeo; and, when he shall die,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2510" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2510"></td>
          <td id="LC2510" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Take him and cut him out in little stars,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2511" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2511"></td>
          <td id="LC2511" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And he will make the face of heaven so fine</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2512" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2512"></td>
          <td id="LC2512" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That all the world will be in love with night</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2513" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2513"></td>
          <td id="LC2513" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And pay no worship to the garish sun.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2514" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2514"></td>
          <td id="LC2514" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O, I have bought the mansion of a love,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2515" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2515"></td>
          <td id="LC2515" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But not possess&#39;d it; and though I am sold,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2516" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2516"></td>
          <td id="LC2516" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Not yet enjoy&#39;d. So tedious is this day</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2517" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2517"></td>
          <td id="LC2517" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As is the night before some festival</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2518" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2518"></td>
          <td id="LC2518" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To an impatient child that hath new robes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2519" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2519"></td>
          <td id="LC2519" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And may not wear them. O, here comes my nurse,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2520" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2520"></td>
          <td id="LC2520" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2521" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2521"></td>
          <td id="LC2521" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">                Enter Nurse, with cords.</td>
        </tr>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2523" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And she brings news; and every tongue that speaks</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2524" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2524"></td>
          <td id="LC2524" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But Romeo&#39;s name speaks heavenly eloquence.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2525" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2525"></td>
          <td id="LC2525" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Now, nurse, what news? What hast thou there? the cords</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC2528" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. Ay, ay, the cords.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2529" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2529"></td>

</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2532" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2532"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC2533" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. Ah, weraday! he&#39;s dead, he&#39;s dead, he&#39;s dead!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2534" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2534"></td>
          <td id="LC2534" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    We are undone, lady, we are undone!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2535" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2535"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC2537" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Can heaven be so envious?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2538" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2538"></td>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC2539" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. Romeo can,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2540" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2540"></td>

        <tr>

        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2542" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2542"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2543" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2543"></td>
          <td id="LC2543" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. What devil art thou that dost torment me thus?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2544" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2544"></td>
          <td id="LC2544" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    This torture should be roar&#39;d in dismal hell.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2545" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2545"></td>
          <td id="LC2545" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hath Romeo slain himself? Say thou but &#39;I,&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2546" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2546"></td>
          <td id="LC2546" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And that bare vowel &#39;I&#39; shall poison more</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2547" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2547"></td>
          <td id="LC2547" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than the death-darting eye of cockatrice.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2548" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2548"></td>
          <td id="LC2548" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I am not I, if there be such an &#39;I&#39;;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2549" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2549"></td>
          <td id="LC2549" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or those eyes shut that make thee answer &#39;I.&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2550" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2550"></td>
          <td id="LC2550" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If he be slain, say &#39;I&#39;; or if not, &#39;no.&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2551" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2551"></td>
          <td id="LC2551" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Brief sounds determine of my weal or woe.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2552" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2552"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2553" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2553"></td>
          <td id="LC2553" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. I saw the wound, I saw it with mine eyes,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2554" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2554"></td>
