          <td id="LC2555" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A piteous corse, a bloody piteous corse;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2556" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2556"></td>
          <td id="LC2556" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Pale, pale as ashes, all bedaub&#39;d in blood,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC2559" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. O, break, my heart! poor bankrout, break at once!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2560" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2560"></td>
          <td id="LC2560" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To prison, eyes; ne&#39;er look on liberty!</td>
        </tr>

        </tr>

</td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2568" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2568"></td>
          <td id="LC2568" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. What storm is this that blows so contrary?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2569" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2569"></td>

          <td id="LC2570" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My dear-lov&#39;d cousin, and my dearer lord?</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="L2571" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2571"></td>

        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2572" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2572"></td>
          <td id="LC2572" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For who is living, if those two are gone?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2573" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2573"></td>
          <td id="LC2573" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2574" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2574"></td>
          <td id="LC2574" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. Tybalt is gone, and Romeo banished;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2575" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2575"></td>
          <td id="LC2575" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Romeo that kill&#39;d him, he is banished.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2576" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2576"></td>
          <td id="LC2576" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2577" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2577"></td>
          <td id="LC2577" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. O God! Did Romeo&#39;s hand shed Tybalt&#39;s blood?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2578" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2578"></td>
          <td id="LC2578" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2579" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2579"></td>
          <td id="LC2579" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. It did, it did! alas the day, it did!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2580" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2580"></td>
          <td id="LC2580" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2581" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2581"></td>
          <td id="LC2581" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. O serpent heart, hid with a flow&#39;ring face!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2582" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2582"></td>
          <td id="LC2582" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Did ever dragon keep so fair a cave?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2583" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2583"></td>
          <td id="LC2583" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Beautiful tyrant! fiend angelical!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2584" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2584"></td>
          <td id="LC2584" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Dove-feather&#39;d raven! wolvish-ravening lamb!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2585" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2585"></td>
          <td id="LC2585" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Despised substance of divinest show!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2586" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2586"></td>
          <td id="LC2586" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Just opposite to what thou justly seem&#39;st-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2587" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2587"></td>
          <td id="LC2587" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A damned saint, an honourable villain!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2588" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2588"></td>
          <td id="LC2588" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O nature, what hadst thou to do in hell</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2589" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2589"></td>
          <td id="LC2589" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    When thou didst bower the spirit of a fiend</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2590" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2590"></td>
          <td id="LC2590" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In mortal paradise of such sweet flesh?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2591" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2591"></td>
          <td id="LC2591" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Was ever book containing such vile matter</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2592" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2592"></td>
          <td id="LC2592" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    So fairly bound? O, that deceit should dwell</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2593" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2593"></td>
          <td id="LC2593" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In such a gorgeous palace!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2594" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2594"></td>
          <td id="LC2594" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2595" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2595"></td>
          <td id="LC2595" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. There&#39;s no trust,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2596" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2596"></td>
          <td id="LC2596" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    No faith, no honesty in men; all perjur&#39;d,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2597" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2597"></td>
          <td id="LC2597" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    All forsworn, all naught, all dissemblers.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2598" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2598"></td>
          <td id="LC2598" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Ah, where&#39;s my man? Give me some aqua vitae.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2599" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2599"></td>
          <td id="LC2599" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    These griefs, these woes, these sorrows make me old.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2600" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2600"></td>
          <td id="LC2600" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shame come to Romeo!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2601" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2601"></td>
          <td id="LC2601" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2602" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2602"></td>
          <td id="LC2602" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Blister&#39;d be thy tongue</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2603" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2603"></td>
          <td id="LC2603" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For such a wish! He was not born to shame.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2604" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2604"></td>
          <td id="LC2604" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Upon his brow shame is asham&#39;d to sit;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2605" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2605"></td>
          <td id="LC2605" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For &#39;tis a throne where honour may be crown&#39;d</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2606" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2606"></td>
          <td id="LC2606" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Sole monarch of the universal earth.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2607" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2607"></td>
          <td id="LC2607" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O, what a beast was I to chide at him!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2608" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2608"></td>
          <td id="LC2608" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2609" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2609"></td>
          <td id="LC2609" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. Will you speak well of him that kill&#39;d your cousin?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2610" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2610"></td>
          <td id="LC2610" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2611" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2611"></td>
          <td id="LC2611" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Shall I speak ill of him that is my husband?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2612" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2612"></td>
          <td id="LC2612" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Ah, poor my lord, what tongue shall smooth thy name</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2613" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2613"></td>
          <td id="LC2613" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    When I, thy three-hours wife, have mangled it?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2614" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2614"></td>
          <td id="LC2614" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But wherefore, villain, didst thou kill my cousin?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2615" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2615"></td>
          <td id="LC2615" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That villain cousin would have kill&#39;d my husband.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2616" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2616"></td>
          <td id="LC2616" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Back, foolish tears, back to your native spring!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2617" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2617"></td>
          <td id="LC2617" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Your tributary drops belong to woe,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2618" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2618"></td>
          <td id="LC2618" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which you, mistaking, offer up to joy.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2619" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2619"></td>
          <td id="LC2619" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My husband lives, that Tybalt would have slain;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2620" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2620"></td>
          <td id="LC2620" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And Tybalt&#39;s dead, that would have slain my husband.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2621" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2621"></td>
          <td id="LC2621" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    All this is comfort; wherefore weep I then?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2622" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2622"></td>
          <td id="LC2622" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Some word there was, worser than Tybalt&#39;s death,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2623" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2623"></td>
          <td id="LC2623" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That murd&#39;red me. I would forget it fain;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2624" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2624"></td>
          <td id="LC2624" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But O, it presses to my memory</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2625" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2625"></td>
          <td id="LC2625" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Like damned guilty deeds to sinners&#39; minds!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2626" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2626"></td>
          <td id="LC2626" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    &#39;Tybalt is dead, and Romeo- banished.&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2627" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2627"></td>
          <td id="LC2627" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That &#39;banished,&#39; that one word &#39;banished,&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2628" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2628"></td>
          <td id="LC2628" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hath slain ten thousand Tybalts. Tybalt&#39;s death</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2629" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2629"></td>
          <td id="LC2629" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Was woe enough, if it had ended there;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2630" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2630"></td>
          <td id="LC2630" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or, if sour woe delights in fellowship</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2631" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2631"></td>
          <td id="LC2631" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And needly will be rank&#39;d with other griefs,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2632" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2632"></td>
          <td id="LC2632" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Why followed not, when she said &#39;Tybalt&#39;s dead,&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2633" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2633"></td>
          <td id="LC2633" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thy father, or thy mother, nay, or both,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2634" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2634"></td>
          <td id="LC2634" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which modern lamentation might have mov&#39;d?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2635" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2635"></td>
          <td id="LC2635" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But with a rearward following Tybalt&#39;s death,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2636" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2636"></td>
          <td id="LC2636" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    &#39;Romeo is banished&#39;- to speak that word</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2637" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2637"></td>
          <td id="LC2637" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is father, mother, Tybalt, Romeo, Juliet,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2638" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2638"></td>
          <td id="LC2638" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    All slain, all dead. &#39;Romeo is banished&#39;-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2639" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2639"></td>
          <td id="LC2639" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    There is no end, no limit, measure, bound,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2640" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2640"></td>
          <td id="LC2640" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In that word&#39;s death; no words can that woe sound.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2641" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2641"></td>
          <td id="LC2641" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where is my father and my mother, nurse?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2642" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2642"></td>
          <td id="LC2642" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2643" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2643"></td>
          <td id="LC2643" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. Weeping and wailing over Tybalt&#39;s corse.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2644" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2644"></td>
          <td id="LC2644" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Will you go to them? I will bring you thither.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2645" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2645"></td>
          <td id="LC2645" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2646" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2646"></td>
          <td id="LC2646" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Wash they his wounds with tears? Mine shall be spent,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2647" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2647"></td>
          <td id="LC2647" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    When theirs are dry, for Romeo&#39;s banishment.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2648" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2648"></td>
          <td id="LC2648" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Take up those cords. Poor ropes, you are beguil&#39;d,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2649" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2649"></td>
          <td id="LC2649" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Both you and I, for Romeo is exil&#39;d.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2650" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2650"></td>
          <td id="LC2650" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    He made you for a highway to my bed;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2651" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2651"></td>
          <td id="LC2651" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But I, a maid, die maiden-widowed.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2652" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2652"></td>
          <td id="LC2652" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Come, cords; come, nurse. I&#39;ll to my wedding bed;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2653" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2653"></td>

</td>

</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2690" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. A gentler judgment vanish&#39;d from his lips-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2691" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2691"></td>
          <td id="LC2691" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Not body&#39;s death, but body&#39;s banishment.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2692" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2692"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC2693" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Ha, banishment? Be merciful, say &#39;death&#39;;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2694" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For exile hath more terror in his look,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2695" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2695"></td>
          <td id="LC2695" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Much more than death. Do not say &#39;banishment.&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2696" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2696"></td>

</td>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC2698" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Be patient, for the world is broad and wide.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2699" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2699"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2700" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2700"></td>
          <td id="LC2700" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. There is no world without Verona walls,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2701" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2701"></td>

        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2702" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2702"></td>
          <td id="LC2702" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hence banished is banish&#39;d from the world,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2703" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2703"></td>
          <td id="LC2703" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And world&#39;s exile is death. Then &#39;banishment&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2704" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2704"></td>
          <td id="LC2704" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is death misterm&#39;d. Calling death &#39;banishment,&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2705" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2705"></td>
          <td id="LC2705" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou cut&#39;st my head off with a golden axe</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2706" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2706"></td>
          <td id="LC2706" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And smilest upon the stroke that murders me.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2707" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2707"></td>
          <td id="LC2707" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2708" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2708"></td>
          <td id="LC2708" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. O deadly sin! O rude unthankfulness!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2709" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2709"></td>
          <td id="LC2709" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thy fault our law calls death; but the kind Prince,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2710" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2710"></td>
          <td id="LC2710" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Taking thy part, hath rush&#39;d aside the law,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2711" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2711"></td>
          <td id="LC2711" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And turn&#39;d that black word death to banishment.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2712" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2712"></td>
          <td id="LC2712" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    This is dear mercy, and thou seest it not.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2713" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2713"></td>
          <td id="LC2713" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2714" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2714"></td>
          <td id="LC2714" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. &#39;Tis torture, and not mercy. Heaven is here,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2715" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2715"></td>
          <td id="LC2715" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where Juliet lives; and every cat and dog</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2716" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2716"></td>
          <td id="LC2716" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And little mouse, every unworthy thing,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2717" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2717"></td>
          <td id="LC2717" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Live here in heaven and may look on her;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2718" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2718"></td>
          <td id="LC2718" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But Romeo may not. More validity,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2719" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2719"></td>
          <td id="LC2719" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    More honourable state, more courtship lives</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2720" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2720"></td>
          <td id="LC2720" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In carrion flies than Romeo. They may seize</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2721" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2721"></td>
          <td id="LC2721" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    On the white wonder of dear Juliet&#39;s hand</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2722" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2722"></td>
          <td id="LC2722" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And steal immortal blessing from her lips,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2723" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2723"></td>
          <td id="LC2723" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Who, even in pure and vestal modesty,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2724" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2724"></td>
          <td id="LC2724" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Still blush, as thinking their own kisses sin;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2725" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2725"></td>
          <td id="LC2725" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But Romeo may not- he is banished.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2726" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2726"></td>
          <td id="LC2726" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    This may flies do, when I from this must fly;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2727" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2727"></td>
          <td id="LC2727" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    They are free men, but I am banished.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2728" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2728"></td>
          <td id="LC2728" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And sayest thou yet that exile is not death?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2729" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2729"></td>
          <td id="LC2729" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hadst thou no poison mix&#39;d, no sharp-ground knife,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2730" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2730"></td>
          <td id="LC2730" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    No sudden mean of death, though ne&#39;er so mean,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2731" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2731"></td>
          <td id="LC2731" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But &#39;banished&#39; to kill me- &#39;banished&#39;?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2732" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2732"></td>
          <td id="LC2732" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O friar, the damned use that word in hell;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2733" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2733"></td>
          <td id="LC2733" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Howling attends it! How hast thou the heart,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2734" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2734"></td>
          <td id="LC2734" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Being a divine, a ghostly confessor,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2735" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2735"></td>
          <td id="LC2735" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A sin-absolver, and my friend profess&#39;d,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2736" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2736"></td>
          <td id="LC2736" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To mangle me with that word &#39;banished&#39;?</td>

</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC2813" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. O, she says nothing, sir, but weeps and weeps;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

        <tr>
          <td id="L2815" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2815"></td>
          <td id="LC2815" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And Tybalt calls; and then on Romeo cries,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2816" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2816"></td>
          <td id="LC2816" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And then down falls again.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2817" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2817"></td>
          <td id="LC2817" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2818" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2818"></td>
          <td id="LC2818" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. As if that name,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2819" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2819"></td>
          <td id="LC2819" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shot from the deadly level of a gun,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2820" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2820"></td>
          <td id="LC2820" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Did murther her; as that name&#39;s cursed hand</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2821" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2821"></td>
          <td id="LC2821" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Murder&#39;d her kinsman. O, tell me, friar, tell me,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2822" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2822"></td>
          <td id="LC2822" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In what vile part of this anatomy</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2823" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2823"></td>
          <td id="LC2823" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Doth my name lodge? Tell me, that I may sack</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2824" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2824"></td>
          <td id="LC2824" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The hateful mansion.                     [Draws his dagger.]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2825" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2825"></td>
          <td id="LC2825" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2826" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2826"></td>
          <td id="LC2826" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Hold thy desperate hand.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2827" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2827"></td>
          <td id="LC2827" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Art thou a man? Thy form cries out thou art;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2828" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2828"></td>
          <td id="LC2828" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thy tears are womanish, thy wild acts denote</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2829" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2829"></td>
          <td id="LC2829" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The unreasonable fury of a beast.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2830" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2830"></td>
          <td id="LC2830" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Unseemly woman in a seeming man!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2831" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2831"></td>
          <td id="LC2831" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or ill-beseeming beast in seeming both!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2832" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2832"></td>
          <td id="LC2832" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou hast amaz&#39;d me. By my holy order,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2833" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2833"></td>
          <td id="LC2833" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I thought thy disposition better temper&#39;d.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2834" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2834"></td>
          <td id="LC2834" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hast thou slain Tybalt? Wilt thou slay thyself?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2835" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2835"></td>
          <td id="LC2835" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And slay thy lady that in thy life lives,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2836" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2836"></td>
          <td id="LC2836" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By doing damned hate upon thyself?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2837" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2837"></td>
          <td id="LC2837" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Why railest thou on thy birth, the heaven, and earth?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2838" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2838"></td>
          <td id="LC2838" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Since birth and heaven and earth, all three do meet</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2839" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2839"></td>
          <td id="LC2839" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In thee at once; which thou at once wouldst lose.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2840" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2840"></td>
          <td id="LC2840" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Fie, fie, thou shamest thy shape, thy love, thy wit,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2841" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2841"></td>
          <td id="LC2841" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which, like a usurer, abound&#39;st in all,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2842" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2842"></td>
          <td id="LC2842" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And usest none in that true use indeed</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2843" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2843"></td>
          <td id="LC2843" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which should bedeck thy shape, thy love, thy wit.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2844" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2844"></td>
          <td id="LC2844" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thy noble shape is but a form of wax</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2845" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2845"></td>
          <td id="LC2845" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Digressing from the valour of a man;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2846" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2846"></td>
          <td id="LC2846" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thy dear love sworn but hollow perjury,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2847" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2847"></td>
          <td id="LC2847" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Killing that love which thou hast vow&#39;d to cherish;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2848" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2848"></td>
          <td id="LC2848" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thy wit, that ornament to shape and love,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2849" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2849"></td>
          <td id="LC2849" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Misshapen in the conduct of them both,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2850" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2850"></td>
          <td id="LC2850" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Like powder in a skilless soldier&#39;s flask,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2851" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2851"></td>
          <td id="LC2851" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    is get afire by thine own ignorance,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2852" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2852"></td>
          <td id="LC2852" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And thou dismemb&#39;red with thine own defence.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2853" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2853"></td>
          <td id="LC2853" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What, rouse thee, man! Thy Juliet is alive,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2854" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2854"></td>
          <td id="LC2854" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For whose dear sake thou wast but lately dead.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2855" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2855"></td>
          <td id="LC2855" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    There art thou happy. Tybalt would kill thee,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2856" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2856"></td>
          <td id="LC2856" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But thou slewest Tybalt. There art thou happy too.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2857" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2857"></td>
          <td id="LC2857" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The law, that threat&#39;ned death, becomes thy friend</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2858" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2858"></td>
          <td id="LC2858" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And turns it to exile. There art thou happy.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2859" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2859"></td>
          <td id="LC2859" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A pack of blessings light upon thy back;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2860" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2860"></td>
          <td id="LC2860" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Happiness courts thee in her best array;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2861" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2861"></td>
          <td id="LC2861" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But, like a misbhav&#39;d and sullen wench,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2862" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2862"></td>
          <td id="LC2862" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou pout&#39;st upon thy fortune and thy love.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2863" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2863"></td>
          <td id="LC2863" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Take heed, take heed, for such die miserable.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2864" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2864"></td>
          <td id="LC2864" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Go get thee to thy love, as was decreed,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2865" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2865"></td>
          <td id="LC2865" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Ascend her chamber, hence and comfort her.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2866" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2866"></td>
          <td id="LC2866" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But look thou stay not till the watch be set,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2867" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2867"></td>
          <td id="LC2867" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For then thou canst not pass to Mantua,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2868" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2868"></td>
          <td id="LC2868" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where thou shalt live till we can find a time</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2869" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2869"></td>
          <td id="LC2869" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To blaze your marriage, reconcile your friends,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2870" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2870"></td>
          <td id="LC2870" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Beg pardon of the Prince, and call thee back</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2871" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2871"></td>
          <td id="LC2871" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    With twenty hundred thousand times more joy</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2872" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2872"></td>
          <td id="LC2872" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than thou went&#39;st forth in lamentation.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2873" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2873"></td>
          <td id="LC2873" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Go before, nurse. Commend me to thy lady,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2874" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2874"></td>
          <td id="LC2874" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And bid her hasten all the house to bed,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2875" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2875"></td>
          <td id="LC2875" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which heavy sorrow makes them apt unto.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2876" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2876"></td>
          <td id="LC2876" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Romeo is coming.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2877" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2877"></td>
          <td id="LC2877" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2878" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2878"></td>
          <td id="LC2878" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. O Lord, I could have stay&#39;d here all the night</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2879" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2879"></td>
          <td id="LC2879" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To hear good counsel. O, what learning is!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2880" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2880"></td>
          <td id="LC2880" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    My lord, I&#39;ll tell my lady you will come.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2881" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2881"></td>
          <td id="LC2881" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2882" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2882"></td>
          <td id="LC2882" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Do so, and bid my sweet prepare to chide.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2883" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2883"></td>
          <td id="LC2883" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2884" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2884"></td>
          <td id="LC2884" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Nurse. Here is a ring she bid me give you, sir.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2885" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2885"></td>
          <td id="LC2885" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hie you, make haste, for it grows very late.           Exit.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2886" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2886"></td>
          <td id="LC2886" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2887" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2887"></td>
          <td id="LC2887" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. How well my comfort is reviv&#39;d by this!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2888" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2888"></td>
          <td id="LC2888" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2889" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2889"></td>
          <td id="LC2889" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Go hence; good night; and here stands all your state:</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2890" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2890"></td>
          <td id="LC2890" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Either be gone before the watch be set,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2891" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2891"></td>
          <td id="LC2891" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or by the break of day disguis&#39;d from hence.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2892" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2892"></td>
          <td id="LC2892" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Sojourn in Mantua. I&#39;ll find out your man,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2893" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2893"></td>
          <td id="LC2893" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And he shall signify from time to time</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2894" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2894"></td>
          <td id="LC2894" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Every good hap to you that chances here.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2895" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2895"></td>
          <td id="LC2895" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Give me thy hand. &#39;Tis late. Farewell; good night.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2896" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2896"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2897" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. But that a joy past joy calls out on me,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2898" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2898"></td>
          <td id="LC2898" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It were a grief so brief to part with thee.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

</td>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC2911" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Cap. Things have fall&#39;n out, sir, so unluckily</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2912" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2912"></td>
          <td id="LC2912" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That we have had no time to move our daughter.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2913" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2913"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC2922" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Lady. I will, and know her mind early to-morrow;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2923" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To-night she&#39;s mew&#39;d up to her heaviness.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2924" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2924"></td>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC2925" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Cap. Sir Paris, I will make a desperate tender</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2926" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2926"></td>
          <td id="LC2926" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of my child&#39;s love. I think she will be rul&#39;d</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2927" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2927"></td>
          <td id="LC2927" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In all respects by me; nay more, I doubt it not.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2928" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Wife, go you to her ere you go to bed;</td>
        </tr>

</td>

        <tr>

</td>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC2952" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Afore me, It is so very very late</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2966" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Wilt thou be gone? It is not yet near day.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2967" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2967"></td>
          <td id="LC2967" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It was the nightingale, and not the lark,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2968" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2968"></td>
          <td id="LC2968" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That pierc&#39;d the fearful hollow of thine ear.</td>

        <tr>
          <td id="L2970" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2970"></td>
          <td id="LC2970" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Believe me, love, it was the nightingale.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2971" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2971"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2972" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2972"></td>
          <td id="LC2972" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. It was the lark, the herald of the morn;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2973" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2973"></td>
          <td id="LC2973" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    No nightingale. Look, love, what envious streaks</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2974" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2974"></td>
          <td id="LC2974" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Do lace the severing clouds in yonder East.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2975" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2975"></td>
          <td id="LC2975" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Night&#39;s candles are burnt out, and jocund day</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2976" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2976"></td>
          <td id="LC2976" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Stands tiptoe on the misty mountain tops.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2977" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2977"></td>
          <td id="LC2977" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I must be gone and live, or stay and die.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2978" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2978"></td>
          <td id="LC2978" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2979" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2979"></td>
          <td id="LC2979" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Yond light is not daylight; I know it, I.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2980" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2980"></td>
          <td id="LC2980" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It is some meteor that the sun exhales</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2981" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2981"></td>
          <td id="LC2981" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To be to thee this night a torchbearer</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2982" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2982"></td>
          <td id="LC2982" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And light thee on the way to Mantua.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2983" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2983"></td>
          <td id="LC2983" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Therefore stay yet; thou need&#39;st not to be gone.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L2984" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="2984"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC2985" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Let me be ta&#39;en, let me be put to death.</td>

          <td id="LC2986" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I am content, so thou wilt have it so.</td>

          <td id="LC2987" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I&#39;ll say yon grey is not the morning&#39;s eye,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC2988" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    &#39;Tis but the pale reflex of Cynthia&#39;s brow;</td>

</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC3056" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Who is&#39;t that calls? It is my lady mother.</td>

        <tr>
          <td id="L3057" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3057"></td>
          <td id="LC3057" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is she not down so late, or up so early?</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td id="L3221" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3221"></td>
          <td id="LC3221" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To have her match&#39;d; and having now provided</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3222" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3222"></td>
          <td id="LC3222" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A gentleman of princely parentage,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3223" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3223"></td>
          <td id="LC3223" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of fair demesnes, youthful, and nobly train&#39;d,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3224" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3224"></td>
          <td id="LC3224" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Stuff&#39;d, as they say, with honourable parts,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3225" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3225"></td>
          <td id="LC3225" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Proportion&#39;d as one&#39;s thought would wish a man-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3226" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3226"></td>
          <td id="LC3226" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And then to have a wretched puling fool,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3227" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3227"></td>
          <td id="LC3227" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A whining mammet, in her fortune&#39;s tender,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3228" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3228"></td>
          <td id="LC3228" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To answer &#39;I&#39;ll not wed, I cannot love;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3229" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3229"></td>
          <td id="LC3229" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I am too young, I pray you pardon me&#39;!</td>

          <td id="LC3230" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But, an you will not wed, I&#39;ll pardon you.</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC3231" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Graze where you will, you shall not house with me.</td>

          <td id="LC3232" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Look to&#39;t, think on&#39;t; I do not use to jest.</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC3233" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thursday is near; lay hand on heart, advise:</td>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC3234" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    An you be mine, I&#39;ll give you to my friend;</td>

</td>

        </tr>

</td>
