          <td id="LC3382" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Ah, Juliet, I already know thy grief;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3383" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3383"></td>
          <td id="LC3383" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It strains me past the compass of my wits.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3384" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3384"></td>
          <td id="LC3384" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I hear thou must, and nothing may prorogue it,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3385" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3385"></td>
          <td id="LC3385" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    On Thursday next be married to this County.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3386" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3386"></td>
          <td id="LC3386" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3387" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3387"></td>
          <td id="LC3387" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Tell me not, friar, that thou hear&#39;st of this,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3388" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3388"></td>
          <td id="LC3388" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Unless thou tell me how I may prevent it.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3389" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3389"></td>
          <td id="LC3389" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If in thy wisdom thou canst give no help,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3390" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3390"></td>
          <td id="LC3390" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Do thou but call my resolution wise</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3391" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3391"></td>
          <td id="LC3391" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And with this knife I&#39;ll help it presently.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3392" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3392"></td>
          <td id="LC3392" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    God join&#39;d my heart and Romeo&#39;s, thou our hands;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3393" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3393"></td>
          <td id="LC3393" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And ere this hand, by thee to Romeo&#39;s seal&#39;d,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3394" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3394"></td>
          <td id="LC3394" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shall be the label to another deed,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3395" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3395"></td>
          <td id="LC3395" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or my true heart with treacherous revolt</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3396" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3396"></td>
          <td id="LC3396" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Turn to another, this shall slay them both.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3397" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3397"></td>
          <td id="LC3397" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Therefore, out of thy long-experienc&#39;d time,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3398" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3398"></td>
          <td id="LC3398" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Give me some present counsel; or, behold,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3399" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3399"></td>
          <td id="LC3399" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    &#39;Twixt my extremes and me this bloody knife</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3400" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3400"></td>
          <td id="LC3400" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shall play the empire, arbitrating that</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3401" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3401"></td>
          <td id="LC3401" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which the commission of thy years and art</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3402" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3402"></td>
          <td id="LC3402" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Could to no issue of true honour bring.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3403" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3403"></td>
          <td id="LC3403" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Be not so long to speak. I long to die</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3404" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3404"></td>
          <td id="LC3404" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If what thou speak&#39;st speak not of remedy.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3405" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3405"></td>
          <td id="LC3405" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3406" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3406"></td>
          <td id="LC3406" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Hold, daughter. I do spy a kind of hope,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3407" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3407"></td>
          <td id="LC3407" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which craves as desperate an execution</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3408" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3408"></td>
          <td id="LC3408" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As that is desperate which we would prevent.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3409" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3409"></td>
          <td id="LC3409" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If, rather than to marry County Paris</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3410" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3410"></td>
          <td id="LC3410" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou hast the strength of will to slay thyself,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3411" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3411"></td>
          <td id="LC3411" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Then is it likely thou wilt undertake</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3412" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3412"></td>
          <td id="LC3412" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A thing like death to chide away this shame,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3413" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3413"></td>
          <td id="LC3413" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That cop&#39;st with death himself to scape from it;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3414" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3414"></td>
          <td id="LC3414" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And, if thou dar&#39;st, I&#39;ll give thee remedy.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3415" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3415"></td>
          <td id="LC3415" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3416" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3416"></td>
          <td id="LC3416" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. O, bid me leap, rather than marry Paris,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3417" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3417"></td>
          <td id="LC3417" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    From off the battlements of yonder tower,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3418" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3418"></td>
          <td id="LC3418" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or walk in thievish ways, or bid me lurk</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3419" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3419"></td>
          <td id="LC3419" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where serpents are; chain me with roaring bears,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3420" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3420"></td>
          <td id="LC3420" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or shut me nightly in a charnel house,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3421" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3421"></td>
          <td id="LC3421" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O&#39;ercover&#39;d quite with dead men&#39;s rattling bones,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3422" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3422"></td>
          <td id="LC3422" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    With reeky shanks and yellow chapless skulls;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3423" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3423"></td>
          <td id="LC3423" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or bid me go into a new-made grave</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3424" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3424"></td>
          <td id="LC3424" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And hide me with a dead man in his shroud-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3425" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3425"></td>
          <td id="LC3425" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Things that, to hear them told, have made me tremble-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3426" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3426"></td>
          <td id="LC3426" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And I will do it without fear or doubt,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3427" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3427"></td>
          <td id="LC3427" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To live an unstain&#39;d wife to my sweet love.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3428" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3428"></td>
          <td id="LC3428" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3429" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3429"></td>
          <td id="LC3429" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Hold, then. Go home, be merry, give consent</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3430" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3430"></td>
          <td id="LC3430" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To marry Paris. Wednesday is to-morrow.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3431" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3431"></td>
          <td id="LC3431" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To-morrow night look that thou lie alone;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3432" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3432"></td>
          <td id="LC3432" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Let not the nurse lie with thee in thy chamber.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3433" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3433"></td>
          <td id="LC3433" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Take thou this vial, being then in bed,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3434" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3434"></td>
          <td id="LC3434" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And this distilled liquor drink thou off;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3435" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3435"></td>
          <td id="LC3435" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    When presently through all thy veins shall run</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3436" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3436"></td>
          <td id="LC3436" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A cold and drowsy humour; for no pulse</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3437" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3437"></td>
          <td id="LC3437" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shall keep his native progress, but surcease;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3438" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3438"></td>
          <td id="LC3438" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    No warmth, no breath, shall testify thou livest;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3439" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3439"></td>
          <td id="LC3439" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The roses in thy lips and cheeks shall fade</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3440" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3440"></td>
          <td id="LC3440" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To paly ashes, thy eyes&#39; windows fall</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3441" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3441"></td>
          <td id="LC3441" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Like death when he shuts up the day of life;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3442" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3442"></td>
          <td id="LC3442" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Each part, depriv&#39;d of supple government,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3443" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3443"></td>
          <td id="LC3443" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shall, stiff and stark and cold, appear like death;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3444" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3444"></td>
          <td id="LC3444" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And in this borrowed likeness of shrunk death</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3445" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3445"></td>
          <td id="LC3445" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou shalt continue two-and-forty hours,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3446" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3446"></td>
          <td id="LC3446" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And then awake as from a pleasant sleep.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3447" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3447"></td>
          <td id="LC3447" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Now, when the bridegroom in the morning comes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3448" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3448"></td>
          <td id="LC3448" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To rouse thee from thy bed, there art thou dead.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3449" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3449"></td>
          <td id="LC3449" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Then, as the manner of our country is,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3450" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3450"></td>
          <td id="LC3450" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In thy best robes uncovered on the bier</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3451" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3451"></td>
          <td id="LC3451" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou shalt be borne to that same ancient vault</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3452" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3452"></td>
          <td id="LC3452" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where all the kindred of the Capulets lie.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3453" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3453"></td>
          <td id="LC3453" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In the mean time, against thou shalt awake,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3454" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3454"></td>
          <td id="LC3454" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shall Romeo by my letters know our drift;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3455" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3455"></td>
          <td id="LC3455" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And hither shall he come; and he and I</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3456" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3456"></td>
          <td id="LC3456" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Will watch thy waking, and that very night</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3457" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3457"></td>
          <td id="LC3457" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Shall Romeo bear thee hence to Mantua.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3458" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3458"></td>
          <td id="LC3458" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And this shall free thee from this present shame,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3459" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3459"></td>
          <td id="LC3459" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If no inconstant toy nor womanish fear</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3460" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3460"></td>
          <td id="LC3460" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Abate thy valour in the acting it.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3461" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3461"></td>
          <td id="LC3461" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3462" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3462"></td>
          <td id="LC3462" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Jul. Give me, give me! O, tell not me of fear!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3463" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3463"></td>
          <td id="LC3463" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3464" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3464"></td>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC3547" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I&#39;ll not to bed to-night; let me alone.</td>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC3611" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The horrible conceit of death and night,</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3621" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3621"></td>

          <td id="L3622" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3622"></td>
          <td id="LC3622" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That living mortals, hearing them, run mad-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3623" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3623"></td>
          <td id="LC3623" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O, if I wake, shall I not be distraught,</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="L3624" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3624"></td>
          <td id="LC3624" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Environed with all these hideous fears,</td>

          <td id="LC3625" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And madly play with my forefathers&#39; joints,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3626" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3626"></td>
          <td id="LC3626" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And pluck the mangled Tybalt from his shroud.,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3627" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3627"></td>
          <td id="LC3627" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And, in this rage, with some great kinsman&#39;s bone</td>
        </tr>

        </tr>

          <td id="L3711" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3711"></td>
          <td id="LC3711" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Sleep for a week; for the next night, I warrant,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3712" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3712"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3793" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3793"></td>
          <td id="LC3793" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Par. Beguil&#39;d, divorced, wronged, spited, slain!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3794" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3794"></td>
          <td id="LC3794" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Most detestable Death, by thee beguil&#39;d,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3795" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3795"></td>
          <td id="LC3795" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By cruel cruel thee quite overthrown!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3796" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3796"></td>
          <td id="LC3796" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O love! O life! not life, but love in death</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3797" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3797"></td>
          <td id="LC3797" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3798" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3798"></td>
          <td id="LC3798" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Cap. Despis&#39;d, distressed, hated, martyr&#39;d, kill&#39;d!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3799" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3799"></td>
          <td id="LC3799" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Uncomfortable time, why cam&#39;st thou now</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3800" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3800"></td>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC3801" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O child! O child! my soul, and not my child!</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC3802" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Dead art thou, dead! alack, my child is dead,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC3805" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. Peace, ho, for shame! Confusion&#39;s cure lives not</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3806" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3806"></td>
          <td id="LC3806" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In these confusions. Heaven and yourself</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC3872" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Pet. Then have at you with my wit! I will dry-beat you with an</td>

        <tr>
          <td id="L3955" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3955"></td>
          <td id="LC3955" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Well, Juliet, I will lie with thee to-night.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3956" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3956"></td>
          <td id="LC3956" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Let&#39;s see for means. O mischief, thou art swift</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3957" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3957"></td>
          <td id="LC3957" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To enter in the thoughts of desperate men!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3958" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3958"></td>
          <td id="LC3958" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I do remember an apothecary,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3959" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3959"></td>
          <td id="LC3959" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And hereabouts &#39;a dwells, which late I noted</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3960" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3960"></td>
          <td id="LC3960" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In tatt&#39;red weeds, with overwhelming brows,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3961" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3961"></td>
          <td id="LC3961" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Culling of simples. Meagre were his looks,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3962" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3962"></td>
          <td id="LC3962" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Sharp misery had worn him to the bones;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3963" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3963"></td>
          <td id="LC3963" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And in his needy shop a tortoise hung,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3964" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3964"></td>
          <td id="LC3964" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    An alligator stuff&#39;d, and other skins</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3965" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3965"></td>
          <td id="LC3965" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of ill-shaped fishes; and about his shelves</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3966" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3966"></td>
          <td id="LC3966" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A beggarly account of empty boxes,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3967" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3967"></td>
          <td id="LC3967" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Green earthen pots, bladders, and musty seeds,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3968" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3968"></td>
          <td id="LC3968" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Remnants of packthread, and old cakes of roses</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3969" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3969"></td>
          <td id="LC3969" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Were thinly scattered, to make up a show.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3970" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3970"></td>
          <td id="LC3970" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Noting this penury, to myself I said,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3971" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3971"></td>
          <td id="LC3971" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    &#39;An if a man did need a poison now</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3972" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3972"></td>
          <td id="LC3972" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Whose sale is present death in Mantua,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3973" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3973"></td>
          <td id="LC3973" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Here lives a caitiff wretch would sell it him.&#39;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3974" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3974"></td>
          <td id="LC3974" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O, this same thought did but forerun my need,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3975" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3975"></td>
          <td id="LC3975" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And this same needy man must sell it me.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3976" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3976"></td>
          <td id="LC3976" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As I remember, this should be the house.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3977" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3977"></td>
          <td id="LC3977" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Being holiday, the beggar&#39;s shop is shut. What, ho! apothecary!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3978" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3978"></td>

</td>
        </tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC3982" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Apoth. Who calls so loud?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3983" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3983"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3984" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3984"></td>
          <td id="LC3984" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Come hither, man. I see that thou art poor.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3985" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3985"></td>
          <td id="LC3985" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hold, there is forty ducats. Let me have</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3986" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3986"></td>
          <td id="LC3986" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A dram of poison, such soon-speeding gear</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3987" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3987"></td>
          <td id="LC3987" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As will disperse itself through all the veins</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3988" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3988"></td>
          <td id="LC3988" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That the life-weary taker mall fall dead,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3989" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3989"></td>
          <td id="LC3989" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And that the trunk may be discharg&#39;d of breath</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3990" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3990"></td>
          <td id="LC3990" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As violently as hasty powder fir&#39;d</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3991" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3991"></td>
          <td id="LC3991" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Doth hurry from the fatal cannon&#39;s womb.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC3993" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Apoth. Such mortal drugs I have; but Mantua&#39;s law</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3994" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3994"></td>
          <td id="LC3994" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is death to any he that utters them.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3995" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3995"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3996" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3996"></td>
          <td id="LC3996" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Art thou so bare and full of wretchedness</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3997" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3997"></td>
          <td id="LC3997" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And fearest to die? Famine is in thy cheeks,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3998" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3998"></td>
          <td id="LC3998" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Need and oppression starveth in thine eyes,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L3999" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="3999"></td>
          <td id="LC3999" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Contempt and beggary hangs upon thy back:</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4000" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4000"></td>
          <td id="LC4000" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The world is not thy friend, nor the world&#39;s law;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4001" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4001"></td>
          <td id="LC4001" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The world affords no law to make thee rich;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4002" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4002"></td>
          <td id="LC4002" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Then be not poor, but break it and take this.</td>
        </tr>

</td>

        </tr>

</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC4008" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Apoth. Put this in any liquid thing you will</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4009" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And drink it off, and if you had the strength</td>

          <td id="LC4010" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of twenty men, it would dispatch you straight.</td>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4012" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. There is thy gold- worse poison to men&#39;s souls,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4013" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4013"></td>
          <td id="LC4013" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Doing more murther in this loathsome world,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4014" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4014"></td>
          <td id="LC4014" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than these poor compounds that thou mayst not sell.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4015" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4015"></td>
          <td id="LC4015" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I sell thee poison; thou hast sold me none.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC4035" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Laur. This same should be the voice of Friar John.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4036" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4036"></td>
          <td id="LC4036" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Welcome from Mantua. What says Romeo?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4037" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4037"></td>
          <td id="LC4037" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or, if his mind be writ, give me his letter.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4039" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4039"></td>
          <td id="LC4039" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  John. Going to find a barefoot brother out,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4040" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4040"></td>
          <td id="LC4040" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    One of our order, to associate me</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4041" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4041"></td>
          <td id="LC4041" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Here in this city visiting the sick,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4042" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4042"></td>
          <td id="LC4042" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And finding him, the searchers of the town,</td>

          <td id="LC4043" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Suspecting that we both were in a house</td>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC4045" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Seal&#39;d up the doors, and would not let us forth,</td>

          <td id="LC4046" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    So that my speed to Mantua there was stay&#39;d.</td>

</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC4050" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  John. I could not send it- here it is again-</td>
        </tr>

</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4055" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4055"></td>

          <td id="LC4056" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of dear import; and the neglecting it</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4057" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4057"></td>
          <td id="LC4057" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    May do much danger. Friar John, go hence,</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4058" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Get me an iron crow and bring it straight</td>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC4066" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hath had no notice of these accidents;</td>

          <td id="LC4075" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">Verona. A churchyard; in it the monument of the Capulets.</td>

          <td id="LC4081" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Yet put it out, for I would not be seen.</td>

          <td id="LC4086" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But thou shalt hear it. Whistle then to me,</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="L4087" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4087"></td>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4090" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Page. [aside] I am almost afraid to stand alone</td>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4093" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Par. Sweet flower, with flowers thy bridal bed I strew</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4094" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4094"></td>
          <td id="LC4094" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    (O woe! thy canopy is dust and stones)</td>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC4095" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Which with sweet water nightly I will dew;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4096" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4096"></td>
          <td id="LC4096" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or, wanting that, with tears distill&#39;d by moans.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4097" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The obsequies that I for thee will keep</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4098" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Nightly shall be to strew, thy grave and weep.</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4100" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The boy gives warning something doth approach.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4101" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4101"></td>
          <td id="LC4101" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What cursed foot wanders this way to-night</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC4103" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What, with a torch? Muffle me, night, awhile.     [Retires.]</td>
        </tr>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4105" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">       Enter Romeo, and Balthasar with a torch, a mattock,</td>
        </tr>

</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC4109" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Give me that mattock and the wrenching iron.</td>

          <td id="LC4111" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    See thou deliver it to my lord and father.</td>

          <td id="LC4112" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Give me the light. Upon thy life I charge thee,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4113" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4113"></td>
          <td id="LC4113" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Whate&#39;er thou hearest or seest, stand all aloof</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4114" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And do not interrupt me in my course.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4115" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4115"></td>
          <td id="LC4115" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Why I descend into this bed of death</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4116" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4116"></td>
          <td id="LC4116" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is partly to behold my lady&#39;s face,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4117" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4117"></td>
          <td id="LC4117" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But chiefly to take thence from her dead finger</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4118" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4118"></td>
          <td id="LC4118" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A precious ring- a ring that I must use</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4119" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4119"></td>
          <td id="LC4119" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In dear employment. Therefore hence, be gone.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4120" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4120"></td>
          <td id="LC4120" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But if thou, jealous, dost return to pry</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4121" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4121"></td>
          <td id="LC4121" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    In what I farther shall intend to do,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4122" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4122"></td>
          <td id="LC4122" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By heaven, I will tear thee joint by joint</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4123" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4123"></td>
          <td id="LC4123" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And strew this hungry churchyard with thy limbs.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4124" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4124"></td>
          <td id="LC4124" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The time and my intents are savage-wild,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4125" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4125"></td>
          <td id="LC4125" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    More fierce and more inexorable far</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4126" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4126"></td>
          <td id="LC4126" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than empty tigers or the roaring sea.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4127" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4127"></td>
          <td id="LC4127" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4128" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4128"></td>
          <td id="LC4128" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Bal. I will be gone, sir, and not trouble you.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4129" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4129"></td>
          <td id="LC4129" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4130" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4130"></td>
          <td id="LC4130" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. So shalt thou show me friendship. Take thou that.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4131" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4131"></td>
          <td id="LC4131" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Live, and be prosperous; and farewell, good fellow.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4132" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4132"></td>
          <td id="LC4132" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4133" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4133"></td>
          <td id="LC4133" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Bal. [aside] For all this same, I&#39;ll hide me hereabout.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4134" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4134"></td>
          <td id="LC4134" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    His looks I fear, and his intents I doubt.        [Retires.]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4135" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4135"></td>
          <td id="LC4135" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4136" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4136"></td>
          <td id="LC4136" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Thou detestable maw, thou womb of death,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4137" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4137"></td>
          <td id="LC4137" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Gorg&#39;d with the dearest morsel of the earth,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4138" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4138"></td>
          <td id="LC4138" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thus I enforce thy rotten jaws to open,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4139" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4139"></td>
          <td id="LC4139" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And in despite I&#39;ll cram thee with more food.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4140" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4140"></td>
          <td id="LC4140" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">                                           Romeo opens the tomb.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4141" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4141"></td>
          <td id="LC4141" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4142" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4142"></td>
          <td id="LC4142" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Par. This is that banish&#39;d haughty Montague</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4143" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4143"></td>
          <td id="LC4143" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That murd&#39;red my love&#39;s cousin- with which grief</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4144" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4144"></td>
          <td id="LC4144" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    It is supposed the fair creature died-</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4145" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4145"></td>
          <td id="LC4145" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And here is come to do some villanous shame</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4146" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4146"></td>
          <td id="LC4146" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To the dead bodies. I will apprehend him.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4147" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4147"></td>
          <td id="LC4147" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Stop thy unhallowed toil, vile Montague!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4148" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4148"></td>
          <td id="LC4148" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Can vengeance be pursu&#39;d further than death?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4149" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4149"></td>
          <td id="LC4149" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Condemned villain, I do apprehend thee.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4150" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4150"></td>
          <td id="LC4150" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Obey, and go with me; for thou must die.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4151" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4151"></td>
          <td id="LC4151" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4152" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4152"></td>
          <td id="LC4152" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. I must indeed; and therefore came I hither.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4153" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4153"></td>
          <td id="LC4153" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Good gentle youth, tempt not a desp&#39;rate man.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4154" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4154"></td>
          <td id="LC4154" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Fly hence and leave me. Think upon these gone;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4155" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4155"></td>
          <td id="LC4155" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Let them affright thee. I beseech thee, youth,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4156" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4156"></td>
          <td id="LC4156" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But not another sin upon my head</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4157" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4157"></td>
          <td id="LC4157" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By urging me to fury. O, be gone!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4158" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4158"></td>
          <td id="LC4158" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    By heaven, I love thee better than myself,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4159" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4159"></td>
          <td id="LC4159" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For I come hither arm&#39;d against myself.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4160" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4160"></td>
          <td id="LC4160" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Stay not, be gone. Live, and hereafter say</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4161" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4161"></td>
          <td id="LC4161" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A madman&#39;s mercy bid thee run away.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4162" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4162"></td>
          <td id="LC4162" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4163" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4163"></td>
          <td id="LC4163" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Par. I do defy thy, conjuration</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4164" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4164"></td>
          <td id="LC4164" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And apprehend thee for a felon here.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4165" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4165"></td>
          <td id="LC4165" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4166" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4166"></td>
          <td id="LC4166" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. Wilt thou provoke me? Then have at thee, boy!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4167" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4167"></td>
          <td id="LC4167" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">                                                     They fight.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4168" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4168"></td>
          <td id="LC4168" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4169" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4169"></td>
          <td id="LC4169" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Page. O Lord, they fight! I will go call the watch.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4170" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4170"></td>
          <td id="LC4170" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">                                            [Exit. Paris falls.]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4171" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4171"></td>
          <td id="LC4171" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4172" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4172"></td>
          <td id="LC4172" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Par. O, I am slain! If thou be merciful,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4173" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4173"></td>
          <td id="LC4173" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Open the tomb, lay me with Juliet.                   [Dies.]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4174" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4174"></td>
          <td id="LC4174" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4175" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4175"></td>
          <td id="LC4175" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Rom. In faith, I will. Let me peruse this face.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4176" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4176"></td>
          <td id="LC4176" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Mercutio&#39;s kinsman, noble County Paris!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4177" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4177"></td>
          <td id="LC4177" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    What said my man when my betossed soul</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4178" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4178"></td>
          <td id="LC4178" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Did not attend him as we rode? I think</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4179" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4179"></td>
          <td id="LC4179" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    He told me Paris should have married Juliet.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4180" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4180"></td>
          <td id="LC4180" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Said he not so? or did I dream it so?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4181" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4181"></td>
          <td id="LC4181" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or am I mad, hearing him talk of Juliet</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4182" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4182"></td>
          <td id="LC4182" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To think it was so? O, give me thy hand,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4183" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4183"></td>
          <td id="LC4183" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    One writ with me in sour misfortune&#39;s book!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4184" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4184"></td>
          <td id="LC4184" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I&#39;ll bury thee in a triumphant grave.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4185" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4185"></td>
          <td id="LC4185" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A grave? O, no, a lanthorn, slaught&#39;red youth,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4186" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4186"></td>
          <td id="LC4186" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For here lies Juliet, and her beauty makes</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4187" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4187"></td>
          <td id="LC4187" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    This vault a feasting presence full of light.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4188" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4188"></td>
          <td id="LC4188" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Death, lie thou there, by a dead man interr&#39;d.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4189" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4189"></td>
          <td id="LC4189" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">                                         [Lays him in the tomb.]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4190" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4190"></td>
          <td id="LC4190" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    How oft when men are at the point of death</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4191" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4191"></td>
          <td id="LC4191" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Have they been merry! which their keepers call</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4192" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4192"></td>
          <td id="LC4192" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A lightning before death. O, how may I</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4193" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4193"></td>
          <td id="LC4193" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Call this a lightning? O my love! my wife!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4194" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4194"></td>
          <td id="LC4194" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Death, that hath suck&#39;d the honey of thy breath,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4195" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4195"></td>
          <td id="LC4195" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Hath had no power yet upon thy beauty.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4196" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4196"></td>
          <td id="LC4196" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thou art not conquer&#39;d. Beauty&#39;s ensign yet</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4197" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4197"></td>
          <td id="LC4197" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is crimson in thy lips and in thy cheeks,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4198" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4198"></td>
          <td id="LC4198" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And death&#39;s pale flag is not advanced there.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4199" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4199"></td>
          <td id="LC4199" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Tybalt, liest thou there in thy bloody sheet?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4200" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4200"></td>
          <td id="LC4200" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    O, what more favour can I do to thee</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4201" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Than with that hand that cut thy youth in twain</td>

          <td id="LC4202" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To sunder his that was thine enemy?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4203" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4203"></td>
          <td id="LC4203" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Forgive me, cousin.&#39; Ah, dear Juliet,</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4204" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Why art thou yet so fair? Shall I believe</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4205" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4205"></td>
          <td id="LC4205" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That unsubstantial Death is amorous,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4206" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And that the lean abhorred monster keeps</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4207" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4207"></td>
          <td id="LC4207" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thee here in dark to be his paramour?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4208" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For fear of that I still will stay with thee</td>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC4209" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And never from this palace of dim night</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4210" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Depart again. Here, here will I remain</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4211" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4211"></td>
          <td id="LC4211" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    With worms that are thy chambermaids. O, here</td>

        <tr>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC4213" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And shake the yoke of inauspicious stars</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4214" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    From this world-wearied flesh. Eyes, look your last!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4215" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4215"></td>
          <td id="LC4215" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Arms, take your last embrace! and, lips, O you</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4216" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4216"></td>
          <td id="LC4216" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The doors of breath, seal with a righteous kiss</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4217" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4217"></td>
          <td id="LC4217" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A dateless bargain to engrossing death!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4218" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4218"></td>
          <td id="LC4218" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Come, bitter conduct; come, unsavoury guide!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

        </tr>

          <td id="LC4220" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The dashing rocks thy seasick weary bark!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4221" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4221"></td>
          <td id="LC4221" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Here&#39;s to my love! [Drinks.] O true apothecary!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4222" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4222"></td>
          <td id="LC4222" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Thy drugs are quick. Thus with a kiss I die.          Falls.</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC4264" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The stony entrance of this sepulchre?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4269" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is guilty of this lamentable chance! The lady stirs.</td>

</td>

        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4276" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. I hear some noise. Lady, come from that nest</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4277" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4277"></td>
          <td id="LC4277" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of death, contagion, and unnatural sleep.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4278" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4278"></td>

          <td id="LC4359" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    These dead men&#39;s tombs.</td>

</td>

        <tr>
          <td id="L4365" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4365"></td>

</td>

          <td id="LC4366" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Wife. O me! this sight of death is as a bell</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4367" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4367"></td>
          <td id="LC4367" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That warns my old age to a sepulchre.</td>

</td>

</td>

</td>

        </tr>

</td>

          <td id="LC4384" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. Seal up the mouth of outrage for a while,</td>

        <tr>
          <td id="L4385" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4385"></td>
          <td id="LC4385" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Till we can clear these ambiguities</td>

          <td id="LC4386" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And know their spring, their head, their true descent;</td>

          <td id="LC4387" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And then will I be general of your woes</td>

          <td id="LC4388" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And lead you even to death. Meantime forbear,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4389" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And let mischance be slave to patience.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4390" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Bring forth the parties of suspicion.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4391" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4391"></td>

</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4392" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4392"></td>
          <td id="LC4392" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. I am the greatest, able to do least,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4393" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4393"></td>
          <td id="LC4393" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Yet most suspected, as the time and place</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4394" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Doth make against me, of this direful murther;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4395" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And here I stand, both to impeach and purge</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4396" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Myself condemned and myself excus&#39;d.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4397" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4397"></td>

</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4398" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. Then say it once what thou dost know in this.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4399" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4399"></td>
