</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4400" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4400"></td>
          <td id="LC4400" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Friar. I will be brief, for my short date of breath</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4401" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4401"></td>
          <td id="LC4401" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Is not so long as is a tedious tale.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4402" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4402"></td>
          <td id="LC4402" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Romeo, there dead, was husband to that Juliet;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4403" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4403"></td>
          <td id="LC4403" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And she, there dead, that Romeo&#39;s faithful wife.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4404" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4404"></td>
          <td id="LC4404" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    I married them; and their stol&#39;n marriage day</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4405" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4405"></td>
          <td id="LC4405" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Was Tybalt&#39;s doomsday, whose untimely death</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4406" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4406"></td>
          <td id="LC4406" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Banish&#39;d the new-made bridegroom from this city;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4407" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4407"></td>
          <td id="LC4407" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    For whom, and not for Tybalt, Juliet pin&#39;d.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4408" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4408"></td>
          <td id="LC4408" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    You, to remove that siege of grief from her,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4409" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4409"></td>
          <td id="LC4409" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Betroth&#39;d and would have married her perforce</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4411" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And with wild looks bid me devise some mean</td>

          <td id="LC4412" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To rid her from this second marriage,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4413" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4413"></td>
          <td id="LC4413" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Or in my cell there would she kill herself.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4414" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4414"></td>
          <td id="LC4414" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Then gave I her (so tutored by my art)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4415" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4415"></td>
          <td id="LC4415" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    A sleeping potion; which so took effect</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4416" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4416"></td>
          <td id="LC4416" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    As I intended, for it wrought on her</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4417" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    The form of death. Meantime I writ to Romeo</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4418" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That he should hither come as this dire night</td>

          <td id="LC4419" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To help to take her from her borrowed grave,</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4420" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Being the time the potion&#39;s force should cease.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4421" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4421"></td>
          <td id="LC4421" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But he which bore my letter, Friar John,</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4422" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Was stay&#39;d by accident, and yesternight</td>
        </tr>

        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4427" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Till I conveniently could send to Romeo.</td>

          <td id="LC4428" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But when I came, some minute ere the time</td>

          <td id="LC4431" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    She wakes; and I entreated her come forth</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

          <td id="LC4432" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And bear this work of heaven with patience;</td>
        </tr>

          <td id="LC4433" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But then a noise did scare me from the tomb,</td>

        <tr>

          <td id="LC4434" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And she, too desperate, would not go with me,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4435" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4435"></td>
          <td id="LC4435" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    But, as it seems, did violence on herself.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4436" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4436"></td>
          <td id="LC4436" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    All this I know, and to the marriage</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4437" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4437"></td>
          <td id="LC4437" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Her nurse is privy; and if aught in this</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4438" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4438"></td>
          <td id="LC4438" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Miscarried by my fault, let my old life</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4439" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4439"></td>
          <td id="LC4439" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Be sacrific&#39;d, some hour before his time,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4440" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4440"></td>
          <td id="LC4440" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Unto the rigour of severest law.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4441" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4441"></td>
          <td id="LC4441" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4442" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4442"></td>
          <td id="LC4442" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. We still have known thee for a holy man.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4443" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4443"></td>
          <td id="LC4443" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where&#39;s Romeo&#39;s man? What can he say in this?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4444" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4444"></td>
          <td id="LC4444" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4445" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4445"></td>
          <td id="LC4445" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Bal. I brought my master news of Juliet&#39;s death;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4446" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4446"></td>
          <td id="LC4446" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And then in post he came from Mantua</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4447" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4447"></td>
          <td id="LC4447" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    To this same place, to this same monument.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4448" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4448"></td>
          <td id="LC4448" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    This letter he early bid me give his father,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4449" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4449"></td>
          <td id="LC4449" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And threat&#39;ned me with death, going in the vault,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4450" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4450"></td>
          <td id="LC4450" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    If I departed not and left him there.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4451" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4451"></td>
          <td id="LC4451" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4452" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4452"></td>
          <td id="LC4452" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. Give me the letter. I will look on it.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4453" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4453"></td>
          <td id="LC4453" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where is the County&#39;s page that rais&#39;d the watch?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4454" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4454"></td>
          <td id="LC4454" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Sirrah, what made your master in this place?</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4455" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4455"></td>
          <td id="LC4455" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4456" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4456"></td>
          <td id="LC4456" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Boy. He came with flowers to strew his lady&#39;s grave;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4457" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4457"></td>
          <td id="LC4457" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And bid me stand aloof, and so I did.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4458" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4458"></td>
          <td id="LC4458" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Anon comes one with light to ope the tomb;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4459" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4459"></td>
          <td id="LC4459" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And by-and-by my master drew on him;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4460" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4460"></td>
          <td id="LC4460" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And then I ran away to call the watch.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4461" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4461"></td>
          <td id="LC4461" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">
</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4462" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4462"></td>
          <td id="LC4462" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Prince. This letter doth make good the friar&#39;s words,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4463" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4463"></td>
          <td id="LC4463" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Their course of love, the tidings of her death;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4464" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4464"></td>
          <td id="LC4464" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And here he writes that he did buy a poison</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4465" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4465"></td>
          <td id="LC4465" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Of a poor pothecary, and therewithal</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4466" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4466"></td>
          <td id="LC4466" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Came to this vault to die, and lie with Juliet.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4467" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4467"></td>
          <td id="LC4467" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Where be these enemies? Capulet, Montage,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4468" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4468"></td>
          <td id="LC4468" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    See what a scourge is laid upon your hate,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4469" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4469"></td>
          <td id="LC4469" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    That heaven finds means to kill your joys with love!</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4470" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4470"></td>
          <td id="LC4470" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    And I, for winking at you, discords too,</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="L4471" class="blob-num js-line-number js-code-nav-line-number js-blob-rnum" data-line-number="4471"></td>
          <td id="LC4471" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">    Have lost a brace of kinsmen. All are punish&#39;d.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>

</td>

</td>

          <td id="LC4477" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line">  Mon. But I can give thee more;</td>
        </tr>

</td>

        </tr>
